DefaultMessage.SourceString:
Oh <b>good.</> 
The bunker guy knows I exist... 
That's <b>exactly</> what I wanted.
I had some next level designs in mind for that <b>spire...</>

Paint won't even stick to it, 
so there goes the Rubble Artist side hustle.
Now it's nothing but piles of <b>shiny rubble.</>
I've <b>seen aliens all my life</>, but now it's like I'm seeing them again for the first time?
It's like <b>falling in love all over again, </>but also like seeing the doctor,

Aliens blast <enemy>the Spire</> into <b>shiny rocks</> and then bang! 
There's the IO
Walkin around with weapons that act just like <b>that ship's laser. </>

<b>ShinyShiny</> rock! 
Aliens make them SOOOO shiny.

Yeah. I've seens some things.
But I'm not telling you <b>anything. </>
